{"tid":1353340,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗市地形口訣：一河兩軌三商場","createTime":"2019-07-23T02:50:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T02:14:28.000Z","uid":265909,"like":86,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"31ecd9afa7671396e79274feb6dde3dfb7b85c7f","tid":1353340,"uid":265909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:50:27.000Z","msg":"小弟屯門大，細個都鍾意去下元朗食野&hellip;&hellip;(下略)<br />\n<br />\n概要<br />\n１）以下係講俾以為元朗大馬路上有牛屎的港九兄弟聽，<strong>屯元天人用返你的方法認路</strong>。<br />\n２）元朗市外可以理解為隨機生怪的野外，當日入野外唔擔保全屍出返黎，但亦唔代表市內唔會生怪。<br />\n３）大部分街地理加功能可分　東西向的橫街　及　南北向的縱街。<br />\n４）元朗有天橋無天橋網絡、無隧道，主要係行地面，唔好期望好似港九咁有仔細指示。<br />\n５）<strong>用指南針</strong>唔好用ＧＰＳ，ＧＰＳ人多樓多好易唔準，而元朗小巷多，側少少都有分別。<br />\n６）背咗口訣佢<strong>「一河兩軌三商場」</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n一河：<strong>臭河</strong><br />\n其實係山貝河延伸入市區的一條渠，姑且叫佢臭河。<br />\n縱向分割元朗市東西兩區，河北有朗屏西鐵站。<br />\n其實一直南延會直通幾個鄉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xfKrkty.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxfKrkty.jpg&h=f2760301&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4QA6ktz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4QA6ktz.jpg&h=e1190b45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔係以下呢兩條。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kep64Vn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkep64Vn.jpg&h=c423c1cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OpB9ifo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOpB9ifo.jpg&h=7c58b22e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩軌：<strong>輕鐵路軌和西鐵路軌</strong><br />\n輕鐵路軌的青山公路元朗段，俗稱元朗大馬路（橫）。<br />\n橫向分割元朗南北兩區。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tr5ibAv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftr5ibAv.jpg&h=ad02f3fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n西鐵路軌的宏達路、媽橫路、朗業街，咁多名其實同一條路黎，簡單Ｄ叫佢西鐵路（橫）。<br />\n橫向的北邊市區邊界。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tpT7Pnh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtpT7Pnh.jpg&h=0c1eac9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三商場&mdash;<strong>ＹＯＨＯ、千色廣場、元朗廣場</strong><br />\n港九人可能聽過的ＹＯＨＯ，連住元朗西鐵站，係市區東邊界線。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eknP2Ho.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeknP2Ho.jpg&h=0da0135e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n右邊係ＹＯＨＯ<br />\n<br />\n千色廣場（好似改左名千色匯）<br />\n大棠路（縱）、教育路（橫）交界。<br />\n因為南邊無明顯分界線，不建議越過千色向南行。<br />\n大棠路亦係去鄉的主要馬路之一。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/trG9ifS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtrG9ifS.jpg&h=b22b491e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n元朗廣場<br />\n大馬路較西位置，斜對面係警署，有天橋直通朗屏西鐵站。<br />\n東邊只有運動場、水邊圍邨、元朗警署，應該只有去警署先會向西越過。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aouSf2D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaouSf2D.jpg&h=41b3c859&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以，可以將元朗市劃分東北、東南、西南、西北４區。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ve64YR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ve64YR.jpg&h=0fe4f690&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n戰略目標：元朗警署<br />\n到達元朗廣場斜對面就係，教育路向西行到盡轉右都可以。<br />\n我諗唔到其他戰略目標。<br />\n<br />\n廁所位或小休點（由東至西）<br />\nＹＯＨＯ（東邊界）<br />\n鳳琴街體育館（東南區，千色和ＹＯＨＯ中間）<br />\n開心廣場（東北區，大馬路邊）<br />\n千色廣場（東南區）<br />\n康樂路元朗兒童遊樂場（東南區，大馬路康樂路輕鐵站轉入去）<br />\n安興遊樂場及元朗圖書館（西南區較南位置）<br />\n大馬路邊元朗廣場（西北區，大馬路邊）<br />\n<br />\n撤退路線<br />\n太多小街，只能講大致方向，不要入小巷，盡量行主要街道，主要街道特徵是平時在過路設施先可以橫過，兩邊有欄杆。<br />\n首先要守住朗屏、元朗兩個西鐵站，因為無路面交通，只能依賴西鐵走。<br />\n後備也只能求義載和踩單車去天水圍，港九人好難做到，唔討論呢個方法了。<br />\n不要向東或向西撤，無交通同埋好易行左去村附近。<br />\n<br />\n向北撤<br />\n一直向北行，直至見到西鐵路軌，<br />\n係西鐵路望，望到邊個西鐵站就去邊個，如果係正路軌下，望到邊個站就係邊個站近。<br />\n<br />\n或者見到元朗廣場去朗屏的天橋，上去或沿橋底向北行，會到朗屏站。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/na3zun3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fna3zun3.jpg&h=3124c35d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n向西撤<br />\n教育路向西行到千色廣場，向北行入大馬路，<br />\n大馬路向西行到ＹＯＨＯ。<br />\n<br />\n光復元朗！"},{"pid":"1201582dd0c4aa6d55e1503c3f8827da381c0c74","tid":1353340,"uid":265909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:08:02.000Z","msg":"輕輕自推一下"},{"pid":"38b8956fc89bda798f9f5a81a27d103b4b6fe7e9","tid":1353340,"uid":164938,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:08:45.000Z","msg":"網上仲有好多人唔知係27定28號<br />\n係改左做27號光復 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wEBdKMw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwEBdKMw.png&h=d464cba0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BoFYVTc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBoFYVTc.png&h=b80a306d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18be8237ae7d99b608f0bae6e138ea3cee8fa6d8","tid":1353340,"uid":158404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:12:49.000Z","msg":"估唔到有一日係用返指南針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42045e5b3771167f4868af437b4abad637ab6259","tid":1353340,"uid":66536,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:13:10.000Z","msg":"千析唔好向南走 入大棠=入左森林"},{"pid":"430cabfdc963ef6e4efe36160d11b82a4d2ab765","tid":1353340,"uid":63124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:17:21.000Z","msg":"去既時候建議各位唔好落單去<br />\n有朋友就搵朋友，冇朋友就tg集齊人先好去"},{"pid":"c8351226548d2ee0b1216885d913e604c872968c","tid":1353340,"uid":106488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:24:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5111ccae08de2e95ed0c271fef658967df95388","tid":1353340,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:35:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ee18ffe486e16adfc9aaf823c7be357069f4a5","tid":1353340,"uid":265909,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:45:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c4d4dbcbe92d16d425b42f6a99a3a41ed2a4b54","tid":1353340,"uid":24045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:51:30.000Z","msg":"實用"},{"pid":"10b7151d0aaa4d6c19789a80c1b9255364cbeaac","tid":1353340,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:54:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0badc9600262946bbfa5e8befe44740ba3f9f6a3","tid":1353340,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:55:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ec6ec5f2793b3cb21d81aaf3a99709aeb0d10ff6","tid":1353340,"uid":167597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:01:33.000Z","msg":"不可向南走"},{"pid":"f765dee1e84394c32f6e08161d0c77f99be6d583","tid":1353340,"uid":34415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:03:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/520eo1h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F520eo1h.jpg&h=32ecfa79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SMbASUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSMbASUF.jpg&h=a2ce6deb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kjPbreK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkjPbreK.jpg&h=068b8664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKrX6eR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKrX6eR.jpg&h=922f47ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/87OcaGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F87OcaGA.jpg&h=5d1b1e66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"448bd6cd36a177aea829752b467c4c4bc5e58fe4","tid":1353340,"uid":265909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:35:05.000Z","msg":"打錯字<br />\n不要向東或向<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">南</span></span></ins></strong>撤，無交通同埋好易行左去村附近。"},{"pid":"6cf38797342a382325f305394371d8fc6e6ff02d","tid":1353340,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:39:56.000Z","msg":"東南西北都唔惦<br />\n<br />\n東 錦田<br />\n南 十八鄉 大棠<br />\n西 屏山 <br />\n(已去屯門要行1個半小時，唔好諗)<br />\n北 死路"},{"pid":"0ce0573785a6182311ea2eb57efccb53e3f1a189","tid":1353340,"uid":265909,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:41:54.000Z","msg":"對唔住各位，打錯字。<br />\n<br />\n撤退路線<br />\n太多小街，只能講大致方向，不要入小巷，盡量行主要街道，主要街道特徵是平時在過路設施先可以橫過，兩邊有欄杆。<br />\n首先要守住朗屏、元朗兩個西鐵站，因為無路面交通，只能依賴西鐵走。<br />\n後備也只能求義載和踩單車去天水圍，港九人好難做到，唔討論呢個方法了。<br />\n不要向<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>西</ins></span></span></strong>或向<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">南</span></span></ins></strong>撤，無交通同埋好易行左去村附近。<br />\n<br />\n向北撤<br />\n一直向北行，直至見到西鐵路軌，<br />\n係西鐵路望，望到邊個西鐵站就去邊個，如果係正路軌下，望到邊個站就係邊個站近。<br />\n<br />\n或者見到元朗廣場去朗屏的天橋，上去或沿橋底向北行，會到朗屏站。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n向<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">東</span></span></ins></strong>撤<br />\n教育路向<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">東</span></span></strong></ins>行到千色廣場，向北行入大馬路，<br />\n大馬路向<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">東</span></span></strong></ins>行到ＹＯＨＯ。"},{"pid":"676cf482f5137b13d7d23d39f8aaefcfa215e314","tid":1353340,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:47:19.000Z","msg":"會唔會有咩逃走最後方案<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n假設真係有人去到夜晚都仲留左係度<br />\n(次次都有咁的情況)<br />\n<br />\n同埋假設元朗，朗屏西鐵站<br />\n無法使用(甚至天水圍)<br />\n例如大規模衝突<br />\n地區戒嚴的可能<br />\n<br />\n大量鄉黑出來打人<br />\n<br />\n東南西北 點都要搵一邊走"},{"pid":"6f89c233e844ca5cbc770910970c0b87d265f17b","tid":1353340,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:49:16.000Z","msg":"唔識路 根輕鐵軌走就實冇錯<br />\n輕鐵軌會經元朗廣場（朗屏西鐵站）同埋yoho（元朗西鐵站）<br />\n根住行 想蕩失路都難"},{"pid":"a78f3afad61b13b282970ce8b441e1ed8e03145e","tid":1353340,"uid":265909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"676cf482f5137b13d7d23d39f8aaefcfa215e314","tid":1353340,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:47:19.000Z","msg":"會唔會有咩逃走最後方案<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n假設真係有人去到夜晚都仲留左係度<br />\n(次次都有咁的情況)<br />\n<br />\n同埋假設元朗，朗屏西鐵站<br />\n無法使用(甚至天水圍)<br />\n例如大規模衝突<br />\n地區戒嚴的可能<br />\n<br />\n大量鄉黑出來打人<br />\n<br />\n東南西北 點都要搵一邊走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:03:53.000Z","msg":"歡迎多Ｄ討論，遲少少改埋錯字方便到時用。<br />\n<br />\n搭西鐵離開元朗站<br />\n其實會停<strong><ins>錦田</ins></strong>先到荃灣西<br />\n要考慮風險，可考慮屯門轉車<br />\n屯門站下巴士站<br />\n60M-&gt;荃灣<br />\n263-&gt;沙田<br />\n961-&gt;上環至灣仔<br />\n再行過屯門市中心總站有<br />\n60X-&gt;美孚至佐敦<br />\nE33-&gt;東涌<br />\nN260-&gt;通宵去荃灣至美孚<br />\n<br />\n半夜係度係真係無安全步行路線<br />\n只能求義載，或者求收留<br />\n小休有朗屏邨，入邊可以玩捉依因"},{"pid":"b0eea2d0e0b340c4f03910dd26a84924905072c6","tid":1353340,"uid":57328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/23/135319_ad08bb8cdcee526bc69c5ee3958d8bf5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F23%2F135319_ad08bb8cdcee526bc69c5ee3958d8bf5.png&h=28c08508&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n元朗勢力分佈圖加大版, 有任何問題隨時回答，持續更新,謝謝"},{"pid":"3c3e533bd74367e6027329937883dd9e84f4d3a8","tid":1353340,"uid":21250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:03:39.000Z","msg":"1.個人認為最多南亞聚集既地方就係合益商場同喜利後面<br />\n<br />\n2.元朗廣場既後面（水邊村），好多老黑係個到食飯<br />\n睇好多老黑搞事既片都係個頭<br />\n<br />\n3.走入朗屏方向去到西鐵站就好，西鐵站之後既地方好似困獸鬥<br />\n<br />\n每年天后誕都係封死哂啲路黎行<br />\n<br />\n元朗既位置真係唔岩遊行"},{"pid":"f96bae8c6d5cd9b291d2e61d4335ef896b56eee1","tid":1353340,"uid":235796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:07:20.000Z","msg":"周街鐵馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef544f34356abc9ae7c79bb12786508c62212ded","tid":1353340,"uid":257712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"676cf482f5137b13d7d23d39f8aaefcfa215e314","tid":1353340,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:47:19.000Z","msg":"會唔會有咩逃走最後方案<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n假設真係有人去到夜晚都仲留左係度<br />\n(次次都有咁的情況)<br />\n<br />\n同埋假設元朗，朗屏西鐵站<br />\n無法使用(甚至天水圍)<br />\n例如大規模衝突<br />\n地區戒嚴的可能<br />\n<br />\n大量鄉黑出來打人<br />\n<br />\n東南西北 點都要搵一邊走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b6e189ae292c80e8b497985ca1e78f0da14141","tid":1353340,"uid":265909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:10:46.000Z","msg":"放定一堆單車係元朗，踩單車去天水圍／屯門<br />\n大家覺得可唔可行"}]}